queryItem.name: FFY Year Qtr
queryItem.expression: 'FFY '||[Business Layer].[Month Dim].[FED_YYYY] ||' '||[Business Layer].[Month Dim].[QTR Name]

queryItem.name: FirstMonth of QTR
queryItem.expression: minimum( [Business Layer].[Month Dim].[Month_Year] for [Business Layer].[Month Dim].[FFY Year Qtr] )

queryItem.name: LastMonth of QTR
queryItem.expression: maximum ([Business Layer].[Month Dim].[Month_Year] for [Business Layer].[Month Dim].[FFY Year Qtr] )

queryItem.name: Month_Year
queryItem.expression: [Business Layer].[Month Dim].[MM] || '/' || [Business Layer].[Month Dim].[YYYY]

queryItem.name: QTR Name
queryItem.expression: case when [Business Layer].[Month Dim].[FED_QTR] = 1 then 'Q1' when [Business Layer].[Month Dim].[FED_QTR] = 2 then 'Q2' when [Business Layer].[Month Dim].[FED_QTR] = 3 then 'Q3' when [Business Layer].[Month Dim].[FED_QTR] = 4 then 'Q4' end

queryItem.name: Quarterly Report Display Format
queryItem.expression: [Business Layer].[Month Dim].[FFY Year Qtr] ||' '||[Business Layer].[Month Dim].[FirstMonth of QTR] ||' - '||[Business Layer].[Month Dim].[LastMonth of QTR]

queryItem.name: FFY Year Qtr
queryItem.expression: 'FFY '||[Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[Federal YYYY] ||' '||[Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[Quarter Name]

queryItem.name: FirstMonth of QTR
queryItem.expression: minimum( [Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[Month Year] for [Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[FFY Year Qtr] )

queryItem.name: LastMonth of QTR
queryItem.expression: maximum ([Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[Month Year] for [Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[FFY Year Qtr] )

queryItem.name: Month Year
queryItem.expression: [Physical Layer].[MONTH_DIM(PARIS)][Physical Layer].[MONTH_DIM].[MM] || '/' || [Physical Layer].[MONTH_DIM(PARIS)][Physical Layer].[MONTH_DIM].[YYYY]

queryItem.name: Quarter Name
queryItem.expression: case when [Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[Federal Quarter] = 1 then 'Q1' when [Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[Federal Quarter] = 2 then 'Q2' when [Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[Federal Quarter] = 3 then 'Q3' when [Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[Federal Quarter] = 4 then 'Q4' end

queryItem.name: Quarterly Report Display Format
queryItem.expression: [Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[FFY Year Qtr] ||' '||[Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[FirstMonth of QTR] ||' - '||[Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[LastMonth of QTR]

queryItem.name: PARIS Reporting Period
queryItem.expression: to_char ([Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[PARIS Quarter Start Date], 'MM/YYYY' ) || ' - ' || to_char ([Business Layer].[Month Dim(PARIS)].[PARIS Quarter End Date], 'MM/YYYY' )

queryItem.name: Person Full Name
Person Full Name
Person Full Name
PI Full Name
Provider Full Name
queryItem.expression:
case
when ([Business Layer].[Provider Dim].[FIRST_NAME] is NULL and [Business Layer].[Provider Dim].[MID_NAME] is NULL) or ([Business Layer].[Provider Dim].[LAST_NAME] is NULL) then (coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Provider Dim].[LAST_NAME] ,'' ) || coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Provider Dim].[FIRST_NAME] ,'' )||' '||coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Provider Dim].[MID_NAME] ,'' ))
else coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Provider Dim].[LAST_NAME] ,'' )||', '|| coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Provider Dim].[FIRST_NAME] ,'' )||' '||coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Provider Dim].[MID_NAME] ,'' )
end

queryItem.name: Worker Full Name
queryItem.expression:
case when [Business Layer].[Worker Dim].[WORKER_ID] = 99 then 'Task Based County'
when ([Business Layer].[Worker Dim].[WORKER_FIRST_NAME] is NULL and [Business Layer].[Worker Dim].[WORKER_MIDDLE_NAME] is NULL) or ([Business Layer].[Worker Dim].[WORKER_LAST_NAME] is NULL) then (coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Worker Dim].[WORKER_LAST_NAME] ,'' ) || coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Worker Dim].[WORKER_FIRST_NAME] ,'' )||' '||coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Worker Dim].[WORKER_MIDDLE_NAME] ,'' ))
else coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Worker Dim].[WORKER_LAST_NAME] ,'' )||', '|| coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Worker Dim].[WORKER_FIRST_NAME] ,'' )||' '||coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Worker Dim].[WORKER_MIDDLE_NAME] ,'' )
end

queryItem.name: Worker Full Name
queryItem.expression:
case when [Business Layer].[Worker Dim(PARIS)].[Worker ID] = 99 then 'Task Based County'
when ([Business Layer].[Worker Dim(PARIS)].[Worker First Name] is NULL and [Business Layer].[Worker Dim(PARIS)].[Worker Middle Name] is NULL) or ([Business Layer].[Worker Dim(PARIS)].[Worker Last Name] is NULL) then (coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Worker Dim(PARIS)].[Worker Last Name] ,'' ) || coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Worker Dim(PARIS)].[Worker First Name] ,'' )||' '||coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Worker Dim(PARIS)].[Worker Middle Name] ,'' ))
else coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Worker Dim(PARIS)].[Worker Last Name] ,'' )||', '|| coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Worker Dim(PARIS)].[Worker First Name] ,'' )||' '||coalesce ( [Business Layer].[Worker Dim(PARIS)].[Worker Middle Name] ,'' )
end
